Package: sensors4plumes
Type: Package
Title: Test and optimise sampling designs based on plume simulations
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2014-11-18
Author: Kristina B. Helle
Maintainer: Kristina B. Helle <kristina.helle@uni-muenster.de>
Description: A package for loading plume simulations (on lattice or points) even if they do not fit into memory, for testing sampling designs by several, flexible cost functions, usually based on the simulations, and for optimising sampling designs using different optimisation algorithms.
License: GPL-3
Imports: lattice, emdist, rgdal, FNN, graphics, conf.design, automap, genalg
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), methods, gstat, sp, raster
